  schema:name "Multi-Currency Accounting" ;
  schema:description "Multi-currency accounting tracks holdings and transactions in more than one currency. This includes foreign currencies, cryptocurrencies, and investment securities — anything denominated in a unit different from your base reporting currency." ;
